%N A395353 a(0) = 0. For n>0, consider the spiral of red and black knights shown in A392177 and A392178. If the n-th square along the negative x-axis contains a black knight then a(n) = n, if it contains a red knight then a(n) = -n, otherwise a(n) = 0.
